g, teaching, scholarship, and research. Fair use is a use permitted by copyright statute that might otherwise be infringing. Non-profit, educational or personal use tips the balance in favor of fair use.','2021-01-23 19:47:30','2021-01-23 19:47:30','Angus','Track Of Doom',NULL,'groq-llm','song name',0.8,'2026-04-04 12:03:21'),(199782,'AXDR6YX801g','Angus Opening Song-Love Spit Love\'s , \"Am I Wrong?',0,0,'The opening song to Angus (Great Movie and Song).\n\nRelease Date:\n15 September 1995','2021-01-23 19:47:30','2021-01-23 19:47:30','Love Spit Love','Am I Wrong',NULL,'groq-llm','song name',0.8,'2026-04-04 12:03:21'),(199783,'8Jmtp5aZHMU','Jackie Oates â€¢ Dream Angus (music video)',0,0,'Music video for Dream Angus from Jackie Oates\' album Lullabies, released March the 18th, 2013.\n\nhttp://www.jackieoates.co.uk\nhttp://www.twitter.com/jackieoates\nhttp://jackieoates.bandcamp.com\n\nFilmed at Merton College and the north parade, Oxford, January 2013.\nDirected by The Boney King Of Nowhere.','2021-01-23 19:47:31','2021-01-23 19:47:31','Jackie Oates','Dream Angus','music video','groq-llm','song name',0.9,'2026-04-04 12:03:21'),(199786,'KY3Prdm_H6E','Angus Stone - Bird On The Buffalo',0,0,'Official Music Video for \"Bird On The Buffalo\" by Angus Stone','2021-01-23 19:47:32','2021-01-23 19:47:32','Angus Stone','Bird On The Buffalo',NULL,'groq-llm','song name',0.9,'2026-04-04 12:03:22'),(199787,'s0gJPPDa1ro','Angus Stone - Broken Brights Official Video',0,0,'The title track from Angus Stone\'s new album Broken Brights out now! Find your copy here: http://t.co/Rz2hMSkv\n\nFind out more about Angus at:\nhttp://www.angusstone.com\nhttp://www.facebook.com/AngusStoneOfficial','2021-01-23 19:47:32','2021-01-23 19:47:32','Angus Stone','Broken Brights','official video','groq-llm','song name',0.9,'2026-04-04 12:03:22'),(199791,'9uIBy71MRQk','Angus & Julia Stone - Harvest Moon - 11/17/2017 - Paste Studios, New York, NY',0,0,'Angus & Julia Stone - Harvest Moon\nRecorded Live: 11/17/2017 - Paste Studios - New York, NY\nMore Angus & Julia Stone in the Paste Cloud: http://www.pastemagazine.com/search?t=Angus & Julia Stone&m=Video\n\nAudio: Bob Mallory\nVideo: Brad Wagner','2021-01-23 19:47:34','2021-01-23 19:47:34','Angus & Julia Stone','Harvest Moon','official','groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199793,'N9_5_Ee2sUs','Angus & Julia Stone - Chateau (Acoustic) - Backstage at ZÃ©nith, Paris',0,0,'NEW ALBUM â€™SNOWâ€™ OUT NOW: https://angusjuliastone.lnk.to/Snow\n \nâ€˜SNOWâ€™ WORLD TOUR - TICKETS // DETAILS - http://www.anagusandjuliastone.com\n \nFilmed and Edited by: Stefan Jose http://www.stefanjose.com\n\nFilmed at ABC Melbourne for The Friday Revue\nhttp://www.abc.net.au/radio/melbourne/programs/thefridayrevue/\nhttps://www.facebook.com/abcmelbourne/\n \nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/AngusAndJulia/\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/angusjuliastone \nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/angusandjuliastone\nWebsite: http://angusandjuliastone.com/\n \nCopyright (C) 2017 Angus & Julia Stone Pty Ltd.\n---\nPowered by http://www.vydia.com\n\nhttp://vevo.ly/YaVJbc\n\n#AngusAndJuliaStone #Chateau #Vevo #Pop #vevoofficial #acoustic','2021-01-23 19:47:34','2021-01-23 19:47:34','Angus & Julia Stone','Chateau','acoustic','groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199794,'zDTaeqUEWNQ','ARGULES - Wellerman (sea shanty) TikTok BUMP HOUSE Remix',0,0,'OUT ON SPOTIFY: https://open.spotify.com/track/1FlFRPgjnA1D5ZTh1EZFl8?si=ZsYQI8MERyqfSjzwETTGhg\n\nhttps://mytrack.online/argules-wellerman-feat-nathan-evanss-luke-g-taylor-1611080520\n\nInstagram: @argules_music\n\nTikTok: @thats.mindblowing @_luke.the.voice_ @nthnevnss\n\nWellerman TikTok Remix','2021-01-23 19:47:35','2021-01-23 19:47:35','ARGULES','Wellerman','remix','groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199798,'n7WxiHoLTQ4','Angus - When Giants Collide (1985) HQ',0,0,'Angus - TV Show 1985 (HQ Sound)\n\nHeavy Metal band from Netherlands\n\nEdgar Lois - Vocals\nBert \"Foxx\" Ettema - Guitars\nWilliam Lawson - Drums \nGerard Carol - Bass\n\nLyrics:\n\nIf Thor\'s hammer is high\nabove the rest \nall the Gods are shivering \nthey know there\'ll be a test \nthe flying monsters \nwith Gorgon as their leader \nare leading to destruction\nEros is fighting either\n \nA giant collision is like\nDamocles his sword \nthey\'re fussing and fighting\njust for fun when they get bored\nWhen Giants collide\nthe lightning is flashing\nand wrathful Gods\nswords are clashing\n\nA giant collision is like\nDamocles his sword\nThey\'re fussing and fighting\njust for fun when they get bored\n\nIf Thor\'s hammer is high\nabove the rest\nall the Gods are shivering\nthey know there\'ll be a test\nWhen giants collide\nthe lightning is flashing\nand wrathful Gods\nswords are clashing\n\n\n*** Saludos desde Colombia, Heavy Metal por siempre!!! ***\n\n\n(Aviso Legal)\n\n---- DISCLAIMER! ----\nCopyright Disclaimer Under Section 107 of the Copyright Act 1976, allowance is made for \"fair use\" for purposes such as criticism, comment, news reporting, teaching, scholarship, and research. Fair use is a use permitted by copyright statute that might otherwise be infringing. Non-profit, educational or personal use tips the balance in favor of fair use.\n**ALL SONGS USED IN THESE VIDEOS BELONG TO THEIR RESPECTFUL OWNERS.\nNO COPYRIGHT INFRINGEMENT INTENDED.','2021-01-23 19:47:36','2021-01-23 19:47:36','Angus','When Giants Collide',NULL,'groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199799,'VEmqd8-sJco','Angus & Julia Stone - Heart Beats Slow (Live Acoustic)',0,0,'Check out our OFFSHORE playlists:\nThe Circle Sessions â­•: http://www.umgt.de/TheCircleSessions\nNew Rock Friday: https://www.umgt.de/NewRockFriday\nAlternative Youth: https://www.umgt.de/AlternativeYouth\nThe Dramatic Scenery: https://www.umgt.de/TheDramaticScenery\nAll that FUZZ: https://www.umgt.de/AllthatFUZZ\n\nOFFSHORE showcases  some of the best alternative music out there - in creative ways.\nSubscribe to our channel http://bit.ly/OFFSHOREYT\n\nLetâ€™s connect:\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/offshore_bln/\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/OffshoreBLN/\nSpotify: https://open.spotify.com/user/midv2rqn2jkp6imnxunkx0ej4?si=z-knOgq8RGCDOvxEFGf8kA\n\n[Verse 1: Angus and Julia]\nWell, I heard you were (you were lying)\nAbout how brave you are\nWell, I heard you were (you were still trying)\nTrying to get back to the start\n\n[Hook: Angus and Julia]\nAnd he won\'t let it into the kitchen\nNo, he won\'t let it into the house\nNo, he won\'t let it through the front door\nCause it\'s burning her pretty little heart\n[Verse 2: Angus and Julia]\nI\'m gonna miss you\nGonna miss you, girl\nAnd all of the things we could have done\nI\'m gonna miss you\nI\'m gonna miss you\nAnd all of the things we should have done\n\n[Bridge: Angus and Julia]\nYou say I move so fast\nThat you can hardly see\nYou say I move so fast\nHow could you be with me?\nBut my heart beats slow\nBut my heart beats slow\nBut my heart beats slow\nBut my heart beats slow\n\n[Verse 3: Angus and Julia]\nWell I wish you, wish you well\nAll the best\nWell I wish you, I wish you well\nAll the best\n\n[Hook: Angus and Julia]\n\n[Bridge: Angus and Julia]\n\n#OFFSHORE #AngusJuliaStone #HeartBeatsSlow','2021-01-23 19:47:36','2021-01-23 19:47:36','Angus & Julia Stone','Heart Beats Slow','live','groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199801,'Ly0fz0T_lQE','Angus & Julia Stone - Paper Aeroplane [Official Music Video]',0,0,'\"Paper Aeroplane\" by Angus & Julia Stone from A Book Like This, available now.\n\nDownload on iTunes: http://smarturl.it/gho1eh\n\nLinks:\nwww.facebook.com/AngusAndJulia\ntwitter.com/angusjuliastone \n\n\"Paper Aeroplane\" Lyrics:\nI spilled the ink across the page trying to spell your name\nSo i fold it up and i flick it out\nPaper aeroplane\nIt wont fly the seven seas to you\nCause it didnt leave my room\nBut it awaits the hands of someone else\nThe garbage man\n\nGot to say mmm mmm mmm x2\n\nSo he opens it up and reads it out to all his friends\nAmongst the crowd a heart will break and a heart will mend\nHe walks on home tired from work\nThe letter falls from his hand\nHe reaches out only to catch the sky\nIts gone with the wind\n\nGot to say mmm mmm mmm x2\n\nI spilled the ink across the land\nTrying to spell your name\nUp and down there it goes\nPaper aeroplane\nIt hasnt flown the seven seas to you\nBut its on its way\nIt goes through the hands\nThen to someone else\nTo find you girl\n\nGot to say mmm Subscribe to Nettwerk\'s YouTube channel: \nhttp://smarturl.it/nettwerkyoutube','2021-01-23 19:47:37','2021-01-23 19:47:37','Angus & Julia Stone','Paper Aeroplane','official','groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199802,'VTW30Q4B3Go','GLORYHAMMER - Angus McFife | Napalm Records',0,0,'Get the CD, Vinyl or Shirt: http://shop.napalmrecords.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=gloryhammer\nGLORYHAMMER is the new project of Christopher Bowes, the mastermind of the Pirate Metal sensation ALESTORM. \"Tales from the Kingdom of Fife\" is a concept album and tells the story of an alternate -history medieval Scotland, a realm of dragons, wizards, magic and dark sorcery. It is the legend of the glorious hero Angus McFife, who wages a long war against the evil wizard Zargothrax, in order to free the people of Dundee. GLORYHAMMER clads these stories in a symphonic Power Metal armor, which will take the listener by storm and will transport them right into the midst of an epic adventure. Pounding doublebass, enthralling riffs and bombastic orchestral parts turn songs like \"The Quest for the Hammer of Glory\" or \"Angus McFife\" into catchy songs that will leave you craving for more. GLORYHAMMER creates the perfect balance between in-your-face speed tracks and epic Metal hymns. A real highlight comes in the form of vocalist Thomas Winkler (EMERALD), whose magnificent voices guides you through the adventure. The album was recorded and produced by Lasse Lammert at the LSD Studios -- the same studio that brought you the classic ALESTORM longplayers! Metal fans should make sure to enter the legendary world of Angus McFife and GLORYHAMMER! Prepare for epic battles!','2021-01-23 19:47:37','2021-01-23 19:47:37','GLORYHAMMER','Angus McFife',NULL,'groq-llm','song title and artist match',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:23'),(199805,'8byd2BcBz8s','Angus Black - Angus Black  (Full Album 2017)',0,0,'Angus Black (2018 Discos Macarras Records)\nhttps://discosmacarras.bandcamp.com/album/angus-black\nVinyl LP (transparent red) limited to 200, also available in our web-store: \nhttps://www.discosmacarras.com/en/vinyls/1851-angus-black-angus-black-lp.html\nhttps://www.facebook.com/discosmacarras/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/discosmacarras/\nDiscos Macarras is based in Catalonia. An Independent Underground Record Label & Distribution. Focused on Doom, Sludge, Rock, Stoner, Metal, Thrash, Death, Grind, Black and other Dark sounds...\n================\nAngus Black (Finland)\nhttp://angusblack.bandcamp.com/\nhttps://www.facebook.com/angusblackband/\n***\n1.\nAll the Sins 00:00 \n2.\nGuide You Home 05:42 \n3.\nI\'m Yours  09:09\n4.\nIncomplete   21:25\n5.\nAcross the Sky   29:42\n6.\nLeaving   34:59\n***\nHeavy Fuzz and groovy stoner doom from gloomy Finland. \n\nTheir members Antti (guitar & vocals), Jyri (bass) and Sampo (drums) are experienced musicians with deep roots in the underground music scene in their native Finland. \n\nJoining forces and combining their individual skills in Angus Black, they believe that have created something special. \n\n***\nThis album was played live and loud at Grain Road Studios in June 2017 and recorded by Ville Keinonen. The tracks were mixed and mastered by Tony Reed at HeavyHead Recording co. All songs and lyrics by Antti. Produced and arranged by Angus Black. Cover art by Jenni VÃ¤re.','2021-01-23 19:47:39','2021-0