\nToo many, too many problems.\nDon\'t know where she belongs, where she belongs.\nShe wants to go home, but nobody\'s home.\nIt\'s where she lies, broken inside.\nWith no place to go, no place to go to dry her eyes.\nBroken inside.\n\n#AvrilLavigne #NobodysHome #Vevo #Pop #OfficialMusicVideo','2021-01-23 19:49:00','2021-01-23 19:49:00','Avril Lavigne','Nobody\'s Home','official','groq-llm','official music video',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200032,'Hd1CQEtrQMY','Bob Marley - Forever Loving Jah',0,0,'Bob Marley - Forever Loving Jah','2021-01-23 19:49:01','2021-01-23 19:49:01','Bob Marley','Forever Loving Jah',NULL,'groq-llm',NULL,1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200034,'ZvS1TUKIbNk','Covenant - Night Of The Blackwinds',0,0,'In Times Before the Light 1997','2021-01-23 19:49:04','2021-01-23 19:49:04','Covenant','Night Of The Blackwinds',NULL,'groq-llm',NULL,1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200035,'KBnMXTSZFxg','DARKTOWER - Dawn (Of Darkened Times)  [OFFICIAL VIDEO]',0,0,'Video for the music \"Dawn of Darkened Times\" taken from the album \"Of Chaos and Ascension\".\n\nProduced by CS Music Videos. \nhttp://www.csmusicvideos.com\n\nDirected and Adapted by Vinicius H. D. Nunes.\nScreenplay by Rodolfo Ferreira.\n\nOrder the album \"Of Chaos and Ascension\" at amazon now! http://bit.ly/ofchaosamazon\n\nSubscribe to Darktower\'s official channel: http://www.youtube.com/user/darktowertv\n\nOfficial Fanpage: http://www.facebook.com/darktowermetal','2021-01-23 19:49:04','2021-01-23 19:49:04','DARKTOWER','Dawn (Of Darkened Times)','official','groq-llm','official video',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200036,'HCNRpNlfzns','Paganizer (Sweden) - The Tower of the Morbid (Death Metal) Transcending Obscurity',0,0,'Taken from the album \'The Tower of the Morbid\' on Transcending Obscurity.  \n\nTranscending Obscurity Store - http://tometal.com/store\nPaganizer Bandcamp - https://paganizer.bandcamp.com\n\nLabel Facebook - http://facebook.com/transcendingobscurityrecords \nBand Facebook - https://facebook.com/paganizersweden\n\nEurope Store - http://transcendingobscurity.aisamerch.de \nUS Store - http://transcendingobscurity.aisamerch.com\n\n\nInfo - \nAfter the success of PAGANIZER\'s landmark album, Land of Weeping Souls, Rogga Johansson and crew have taken things up a notch, working harder than ever before to present an album with the best possible qualities that the band is known for over the years. Featuring jaw-dropping artwork from the master himself, Dan Seagrave, steps have been taken to ensure that nothing falls short with this release in any way. Musically, it\'s the same crushing death metal machine laden with catchy hooks and riffs that embed themselves in your memory for aeons while ever so deftly switching tempos without letting go of the brutality. This here is Swedish death metal at its finest. The maniacal rush is tempered beautifully with reflective leads and shades of wistful melancholy, which is something Rogga Johansson is getting adept at, as evidenced by his recent solo band material. The Tower of the Morbid stands tall among its peers for creating timeless, perfected death metal meant for fans of all schools, old and new. \n\n\nLine up - \nRogga Johansson - Vocals, Guitars \nMartin Klasen - Bass \nMatte Fiebig - Drums \nKjetil Lynghaug - Lead Guitars \n\nLayout by Turkka Rantanen (ROGGA JOHANSSON, DEMILICH)','2021-01-23 19:49:05','2021-01-23 19:49:05','The Tower of the Morbid','Paganizer',NULL,'groq-llm-corrected','Auto-corrected swapped artist/track by title order: HCNRpNlfzns',1,'2026-04-08 10:12:50'),(200038,'-B8A1To_-8Y','Black Sabbath- Vol. 4- Under The Sun',0,0,'','2021-01-23 19:49:05','2021-01-23 19:49:05','Black Sabbath','Under The Sun',NULL,'groq-llm',NULL,1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200040,'48DVwXeu40w','Cassiane 25 Anos Ao Vivo Hino da VitÃ³ria',0,0,'Musica do Dvd Cassiane 25 anos de muito Louvor','2021-01-23 19:49:06','2021-01-23 19:49:06','Cassiane','Hino da VitÃ³ria','live','groq-llm','live album',1,'2026-04-04 12:03:44'),(200042,'1F